{"tid":136251,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"醒啦香港人！！不正當運用政治勢力","createTime":"2017-02-27T02:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T11:07:00.000Z","uid":58984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2f09df907f762e26d7ac3f92dc0bbe5fb4d0e0","tid":136251,"uid":58984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T02:31:50.000Z","msg":"其實唔理熱狗/葉狗事件<br />\n我地都可以發現真正既當權者既威力<br />\n何謂真正當權者，香港為例689？<br />\n錯，係能夠煽動人群既當權者<br />\n人類就係因為有情感，因而需要規則約束<br />\n從葉狗既盲反可以睇到好多人唔追查事實<br />\n就盲目去撐，去投訴，去施壓<br />\n令我記起最近日本夫婦開鋪，比一個客搞到放棄打算返日本<br />\n一個人力量如是，何況擁有政治勢力既佢地<br />\n雖則，<br />\ncafe班人都傻下傻下，中伏拉本土牌頭<br />\n但係依種不正當私怨行為，真係要打擊下<br />\n我認我曾經係狗，但我做返人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一人一個report或留言，或可能阻嚇到收斂下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b3af2db4b3b52dba0eed3a3dbd0a1b6c97bb4e","tid":136251,"uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"都係個句，今次撐葉狗班人柒哂<br />\n點解廢中會支持七警，點解會反對人遊行示威？<br />\n因為無釐清事實真相，亦都唔敢去查<br />\n點解唔查？因為權力<br />\n就如米爾格倫實驗一樣，<br />\n真真正正令自己變左隻狗<br />\n撐葉狗班人同廢中無任何分別。"},{"pid":"84f1f31b79502efd1be3353f1d5fcc8a899b9ff9","tid":136251,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:24:58.000Z","msg":"好彩9月4後已經離教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac165fca0818d3778cf181e76bca3d001ca4598f","tid":136251,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:21:38.000Z","msg":"呢啲通常叫黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62dda2a766f2a98aa0ff5b224343a0a0530aa1e9","tid":136251,"uid":58984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"